            </li>

            <li>
              <h3 class="title is-4">Dockerizing Vue App</h3>
              <p>In this chapter, you will learn the nitty-gritty involved in dockerizing your Vue project. In addition, you will learn best practices and industry-standard to dockerize and deploy an enterprise Vue.js 3 web application. This chapter will also go more practical by dockerizing a full-stack web application and deploying the container to a cloud platform using Docker Compose. You will learn how to handle larger projects with Docker Compose.</p>
